<div class='panel header'>
  <% if current_user %>
    <span>Hello, <%= current_user.display_name %>!</span>
    <ul>
      <% if @is_admin %>
        <li><%= link_to 'Add/Edit Post', ratrace_posts_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Home', greghome_path %></li>
      <% end %>
      <li><%= link_to 'Sign Out', destroy_user_session_path, method: 'DELETE' %></li>
    </ul>
  <% else %>
    <span>You're not signed in.</span>
    <ul>
      <li><%= link_to "Sign in with Facebook", user_facebook_omniauth_authorize_path %></li>
    </ul>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class='panel countdown'>

  <div class='timer-element'>
    <span class="digit weeks">&nbsp;</span>
    <span>Weeks</span>
  </div>

  <div class='timer-element'>
    <span class="digit days">&nbsp;</span>
    <span>Days</span>
  </div>

  <div class='timer-element'>
    <span class="digit hours">&nbsp;</span>
    <span>Hours</span>
  </div>

  <div class='timer-element'>
     <span class="digit minutes">&nbsp;</span>
    <span>Minutes</span>
  </div>

  <div class='timer-element'>
    <span class="digit seconds">&nbsp;</span>
    <span>Seconds</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="panel intro collapsed">
  <ul class="center">
    <li><a class="expander">Read all about it...</a></li>
    <li><%= link_to "Our Justgiving Page", "https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/greg-jo-shailes", target: :blank %></li>
    <li><%= link_to "RatRace Site", "http://ratrace.com/coasttocoast/", target: :blank %></li>
  </ul>

  <%= image_tag 'C2C_20182-black-background.png' %>

  <p>In September 2018, we will be taking part in the Rat Race 'Coast to Coast' challenge, a two-day, 105-mile cycling, kayaking and running journey across the Scottish highlands.</p>

  <p>We're hoping to raise money for Macmillan Cancer Care. We were both so grateful for the support Macmillan nurses gave us through Greg's illness last year and want to be able to help Macmillan help more people through difficult times.</p>

  <p>Have a look at the <%= link_to "Rat Race web site", "http://ratrace.com/coasttocoast/", target: :blank %> to see what the event's all about. It's going to be a massive challenge for us. Neither of us are runners, and the chances of us co-ordinating ourselves together to propel a kayak in a straight line are pretty minimal. We're going to have to do a lot of training over the next ten months to get ourselves fit enough to complete the event. Keep an eye on this page for updates on how we're getting along!</p>

  <p>Check out our <%= link_to "Just Giving page", "https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/greg-jo-shailes", target: :blank %> if you'd like to sponsor us!</p>

</div>

<% alternate = false %>
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <h1 class='panel-header'><%= post.title %></h1>
  <h2 class='panel-sub-header'><%= post.pretty_created_at %> by <%= post.user.first_name %></h2>

  <div class='panel-body'>
    <% if post.image %>
      <%= ('<img %ssrc="data:image/jpg;base64,%s">' % [(alternate ? '' : 'class="alternate" '), Base64.encode64(post.image.filedata)]).html_safe %>
      <% alternate = !alternate %>
    <% end %>
    <%= sanitize(post.formatted_body, tags: %w(p)) %>
    <% post.comments.each do |comment| %>
      <% comment_decorator = ::CommentDecorator.new(comment) %>
      <div class='comment'>
        <% if @current_user == comment.user %>
          <%= link_to(ratrace_post_comment_path(post, comment), method: :delete, class: 'delete-comment', data: {confirm: 'Delete your comment?'}) do %>
            <i class="fa fa-close"></i>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
        &ldquo;<%= comment.comment %>&rdquo;
        <span><%= comment_decorator.commenter_name %>, <%= comment_decorator.humanized_recency %></span>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <% if @current_user %>
      <div class='comment'>
        <%= form_for :ratrace_post_comment, :url => ratrace_post_comments_path(post) do |f| %>
          <%= f.text_field :comment, placeholder: (post.comments.any? ? 'Add your comment' : 'Be the first to comment!'), class: 'comment_box' %>
          <%= f.submit 'OK', class: 'tick-btn' %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <div class="login_to_comment">
        <%= link_to "Log in with Facebook", user_facebook_omniauth_authorize_path %> to comment
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
<% end %>
